  • public class EventAbstractionManager
extends java.lang.Object
    An EventAbstractionManager provides functionalities for generation of AbstractEvents in an AbstractModel from the informations provided by a SBML Model.
    The EventAbstractionManager works under the assumption that the SBML Model has been pre-processed with a ModelPreprocessingManager.
